snippet.title: Nihongo Quest on Steam Trailer
snippet.description: Learn Japanese through gaming! Nihongo Quest N5 is a colorful JRPG that will teach you over 1000 Japanese words and characters. Explore the world of Gakushū as you battle, race, and draw your way to victory! Teaches up to the JLPT N5 level of Japanese.
